To support and commemorate the victory of Demola Babalola at the recently held Nigeria Union of Journalists (NUJ) elections Oyo State chapter, the management of Kayrom Lee Gym and fitness center has announced free medical checkups and gym session for Oyo NUJ members. This was disclosed in a congratulatory message by the CEO of Kayrom Lee, Amb. Romoke Ayinde while  congratulating Babalola. “As they say that ‘health is wealth we want to show our support to the new NUJ boss being our friend in the sporting family by managing the health of their members. “Considering the busy nature of a journalist, we shall offer all members of Oyo NUJ free medical checkups which includes: high blood pressure test, blood sugar and ECG with free gym session”, the statement reads.